Tuesday, February 24, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-822. State v. Zucal.

Stark App. No. 1996CA00179. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Stark County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to participate in oral argument currently scheduled for March 24,1998,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to participate in oral argument be, and hereby is, denied.
